org.opendatafoundation.data.spss.SPSSFileException

Packages that use SPSSFileException
org.opendatafoundation.data.spss Provides the classes necessary to read SPSS .sav data files to (1) produce DDI 2.0 and DDI 3.0 XML metadata and (2) export the data into ASCII format.
